ces==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Limwanya, Milika}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women's association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Zambian women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Zambia women's international footballers]]\n[[Category:ZESCO United F.C. players]]\n\n\n{{Zambia-women-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Zambian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Milika Limwanya\n| image          = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = \n| birth_place    = {{Birth date and age|1996|1|8|df=y}}<ref name=CAF>{{Cite web|url=http://admin.cafonline.com/en-us/competitions/africanwomenchampionship,cameroon2016/TeamDetails/playerdetails?CompetitionPlayerId=KFf%2fRl%2fJfpGoINx4%2f2cZTgl7AVr0g83TgzUp4rg6HJaKpVIWGJlpY0SAByLnGpDz|website=CAF|title=Competitions - African Women Championship, Cameroon 2016 - Team Details - Player Details|accessdate=12 March 2020}}</ref>\n| height         = \n| position       = [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|Defensive midfielder]]<ref name=DMZM>{{Cite web|url=http://www.daily-mail.co.zm/milika-limwanya-defensive-midfielder-craving-success/|title=Milika Limwanya: A defensive midfielder craving for success|date=19 February 2016|accessdate=12 March 2020|first=Diana|last=Mutakafimbo}}</ref>\n| currentclub    = \n| clubnumber     = \n| years1         =\n| clubs1         = [[ZESCO United F.C.|ZESCO United]]\n| nationalyears1 = 2017\n| nationalteam1  = [[Zambia women's national football team|Zambia]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 1+\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| ntupdate       = 21 September 2017\n}}\n'''Milika Limwanya''' (born 8 January 1996) is a Zambian [[Women's association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]]. She has been a member of the [[Zambia women's national football team|Zambia women's national team]].\n\n==Club career==\nLimwanya has played for [[ZESCO United F.C.|ZESCO United FC]].<ref name=DMZM/>\n\n==International career==\nLimwanya capped for Zambia at the [[2017 COSAFA Women's Championship]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.goalshouter.com/matches/76628|title=Zambia Women \u2013 South Africa Women|website=GoalShouter|date=21 September 2017|accessdate=12 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Limwanya, Milika}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women's association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Zambian women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Zambia women's international footballers]]\n[[Category:ZESCO United F.C. players]]\n", "name_user": "Joeykai", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up, addedorphantag", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milika_Limwanya"}
